site.name: Wistia
site.htmlBelowHeader: Welcome to Wistia's home for real-time information and updates on our applications. Here you'll find live and historical data on system performance and metrics. If there are any service interruptions, a note will be posted here.

updates.message: We've identified why stats processing was delayed and have restarted processing new stats for videos as of an hour ago. We will be backfilling stats over the next few days due to volume, so stats may be lower for 2023-06-03 until this operation is complete.
updates.messageHtml: We've identified why stats processing was delayed and have restarted processing new stats for videos as of an hour ago. We will be backfilling stats over the next few days due to volume, so stats may be lower for 2023-06-03 until this operation is complete.

activeIncidents.name: Some podcast episode analytics may be incorrect

updates.message: In addition to incorrect podcast stats from 4/26-5/3, we are also aware of missing stats for some podcast episodes from 5/3-5/9. We are working on correcting and backfilling podcast stats for this entire period.
updates.messageHtml: In addition to incorrect podcast stats from 4/26-5/3, we are also aware of missing stats for some podcast episodes from 5/3-5/9. We are working on correcting and backfilling podcast stats for this entire period.

updates.message: We implemented a fix that should correct all newly received "plays" and "played time" stats, although those stats will still potentially be incorrect from 4/26 through 5/3. We continue work to correct the data from that period.
updates.messageHtml: We implemented a fix that should correct all newly received "plays" and "played time" stats, although those stats will still potentially be incorrect from 4/26 through 5/3. We continue work to correct the data from that period.

updates.message: The played time statistic for all podcast episodes should be considered unreliable beginning on 4/26. In addition, reported plays during that period may be lower than the actual number. We are continuing to work on a fix.
updates.messageHtml: The played time statistic for all podcast episodes should be considered unreliable beginning on 4/26. In addition, reported plays during that period may be lower than the actual number. We are continuing to work on a fix.

updates.message: We have received reports of podcast episodes having a negative "played time" statistic, beginning on 4/26. We are actively working on a fix for this issue.
updates.messageHtml: We have received reports of podcast episodes having a negative "played time" statistic, beginning on 4/26. We are actively working on a fix for this issue.

updates.message: We will be performing maintenance on our analytics databases. Intermittent unavailability of certain stats-related functions in the Wistia application during the maintenance period should be expected.
updates.messageHtml: We will be performing maintenance on our analytics databases. Intermittent unavailability of certain stats-related functions in the Wistia application during the maintenance period should be expected.

updates.message: As part of improving our security posture, we will be disabling the ability to connect to fast.wistia.com or fast.wistia.net using TLS 1.0/1.1 connections on July 3rd. These endpoints are used for loading video embed metadata required by our player to play videos embedded on webpages across the web. Most web browsers/operating systems/devices from 2014 forwards should be utilizing TLS 1.2/1.3 to connect and load Wistia embeds.
